name: Genuine Genie
projectDescription: A bot that can do everything? Yes you read that right, this is an advanced community server setup/management/moderation/handling discord-bot with about 50+ commands and 10+ features!! Set up any channel as a welcome channel with your own custom message. When anyone joins, the bot will auto greet with your custom text. You can set up any channel with the thank's leaderboard and the top 30 people who have been thanked will be displyed in this channel, refreshing every 30 mins. This is a fun way to motivate your server members to help out others. Set up any channel to auto-poll any message sent in case you require a lot of community opinion. When someone sends a message <emoji> = <content>, the bot will auto add those emojis to the message sent. So people can now easily voice their opinions by simply reacting to the message. Set up any channel as the role-claim channel. Once you finish up assigning roles to emojis, you can create a role claim channel and leave the bot to take care of the rest. Emojis that represent roles are automatically added and then comes the Magical part!! When people react, they GET THE ROLE! Set up any channel as suggestions channel, once set up, any message you send here will be auto styled into an aesthetic template awaiting community feedback. Moderators can then accept or deny a suggestion with basic commands. GG also lets you set up a channel to log everything that a person with the role 'Moderator' would say, It's an effective tool to moderate anything and everything that a 'Moderator' says in your server. The features of GG bot doesn't stop here, it's now an open source project and if you would like to contribute check out the github repo!
